Sanidassanattika, Saññojanadukādi
107.
261Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ saññojanaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho nosaññojano dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
262Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi…pe…  avigate cha.
